    <text>
        <body>
            <pb facs="MSIAsheet21"/>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l><handShift corresp="#HANDJJR" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>The way was long &#x0026; yet twas sweet<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">25</add></l>
                    <l>Thro many a shady soft retreat</l>
                    <l>Where the broad willow semblance gave</l>
                    <l>of Weeping Beauty in the Wave</l>
                    <l>And Elm with massy foliage pressed</l>
                    <l>And feathery aspens quivering Crest<add place="margin-right">3<supplied>0</supplied></add></l>
                    <l>And many a spiry poplar glade</l>
                    <l>And Hazels rich Entangled shade</l>
                    <l>While onward as advancing still</l>
                    <l>From <placeName corresp="#STOMER">Omers</placeName> plain<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#STOMERSPLAINGLOSS"/> to <placeName corresp="#CASSEL">Cassell</placeName>s hill<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#CASSELSHILLGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Far yet more far the Landscape threw</l>
                    <l>Its deep immeasurable Blue</l>
                    <l>Oh beautiful those plains were <lb type="runover" rend="below"/><space quantity="22" unit="chars"/>showing</l>
                    <l>Where Summers Sun was hotly glowing</l>
                    <l>Many a Battle field lay spread</l>
                    <l>Once the dark Dwelling of the Dead</l>
                    <l>But fruitful now their Champaigns<lb type="runover" rend="below"/><space quantity="31" unit="chars"/>wave</l>
                    <l>With bending Grain on soldiers Grave</l>
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>While far beneath in long array</l>
                    <l>The priestly orders wound their way<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#PRIESTLYORDERSGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Heavy the massive banners rolled<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">45</add></l>
                    <l>Rich wrought with gems and stiff with gold</l>
                    <l>While as the cross came borne on high</l>
                    <l>Beneath its crimson canopy</l>
                    <l>Many the haughty head that bowed</l>
                    <l>Sunk his high crest the warrior proud<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">50</add></l>
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough">T</del> The priest his glance benignant cast</l>
            <pb facs="1038179r"/>
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>And murmured blessings as he past</l>
                    <l>While round the hillside echoing free</l>
                    <l>Rung the loud hymning melody.</l>
                    <l>Many a monkish voice was there<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">55</add></l>
                    <l>Many a trumpet rent the <del rend="strikethrough">Aar</del> air</l>
                    <l>And softer, sweeter, yet the same</l>
                    <l>The sounds in failing cadence came.</l>
                    <l>No marvel, that the pomp and pride</l>
                    <l>Of <placeName corresp="#ROME">Rome</placeName>s religion thus should hide<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">60</add></l>
                    <l>The serpent folds beneath that roll</l>
                    <l>The poison mantling in the bowl<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#NOMARVEL"/></l>
                </lg>
  
            </div>
